cd /home/snops/f5-rs-aws-app/ && ansible-playbook --vault-password-file ~/.vault_pass.txt \ playbooks/aws_app_deploy.yaml -e "\ aws_region="$(etcdctl get f5-rs-aws-net/98072100/aws_region)" \ applicationSubnets="$(etcdctl get f5-rs-aws-net/98072100/applicationSubnets)" \ deploymentName=98072100 \ service_name=App1 \ vpc="$(etcdctl get f5-rs-aws-net/98072100/vpc)" \ state=absent"
cd /home/snops/f5-rs-aws-external-lb/ && ansible-playbook --vault-password-file ~/.vault_pass.txt \ playbooks/aws_external_elb_deploy.yaml -e "\ deploymentName=98072100 \ service_name=App1 \ aws_region="$(etcdctl get f5-rs-aws-net/98072100/aws_region)" \ vpc="$(etcdctl get f5-rs-aws-net/98072100/vpc)" \ subnets="$(etcdctl get f5-rs-aws-net/98072100/subnets)" \ state=absent"
cd /home/snops/f5-rs-aws-net/ && ansible-playbook --vault-password-file ~/.vault_pass.txt \ playbooks/aws_net_deploy.yaml -e "\ deploymentName=98072100 \ aws_region=us-west-2 \ state=absent"
